{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781719663272,"sessionID":"ses_1293d8f52ffeq7LR48U3s4YG7N","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_2ae776c35f8c4cde9c2dbc3c","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p019-mimo-1/deep-review-strategy.md","content":"---\ntitle: \"Deep Review Strategy: maintenance-grace daemon survives re-election\"\ndescription: \"Strategy document for the deep review loop on spec 019-maintenance-grace-daemon-survives-reelection\"\n---\n\n# Deep Review Strategy\n\n## Topic\n\nReview of spec 019: maintenance-grace daemon survives re-election. The daemon writes a refreshed `.maintenance-active.json` marker during background scans so competing launchers adopt a busy-but-healthy daemon instead of reaping it.\n\n## Review Dimensions\n\n- [x] D1 Correctness — reviewed (iteration 1)\n- [ ] D2 Security — pending\n- [ ] D3 Traceability — pending\n- [ ] D4 Maintainability — pending\n\n## Files Under Review\n\n| File | Path | Status |\n|------|------|--------|\n| Daemon marker writer | `.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/lib/storage/maintenance-marker.ts` | reviewed |\n| Pure supervision predicate | `.opencode/bin/lib/model-server-supervision.cjs` (lines 600-640) | reviewed |\n| Launcher guard (dead-socket) | `.opencode/bin/mk-spec-memory-launcher.cjs` (lines 810-825) | reviewed |\n| Launcher guard (stale-reclaim) | `.opencode/bin/mk-spec-memory-launcher.cjs` (lines 1685-1694) | reviewed |\n| Unit test | `.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/tests/launcher-maintenance-guard.vitest.ts` | reviewed |\n| Isolated harness | `.opencode/skills/system-spec-kit/mcp_server/stress_test/durability/daemon-reelection-adoption-live.vitest.ts` | reviewed |\n| Spec doc | `.opencode/specs/.../019-.../spec.md` | reviewed |\n| Implementation summary | `.opencode/specs/.../019-.../implementation-summary.md` | reviewed |\n| Plan | `.opencode/specs/.../019-.../plan.md` | reviewed |\n| Tasks | `.opencode/specs/.../019-.../tasks.md` | reviewed |\n\n## Cross-Reference Status\n\n### Core Protocols\n\n| Protocol | Status | Notes |\n|----------|--------|-------|\n| `spec_code` | partial | Spec says `jobId` in marker; code uses `labels` array. Spec says 60s TTL; code uses 180s. Spec says key_files are under `mcp_server/bin/`; actual path is `.opencode/bin/`. |\n| `checklist_evidence` | skipped | No `checklist.md` exists (Level 1 spec) |\n\n### Overlay Protocols\n\nNone applicable for spec-folder target type at Level 1.\n\n## Known Context\n\n- Spec is Level 1, status \"Complete (code)\", completion 100%.\n- No `resource-map.md` present. Skipping coverage gate.\n- Predecessor spec 018 made background scans cooperative; this phase ensures the daemon survives launcher contention during a scan.\n- The implementation summary documents a live run where a full reindex completed in 330s without the daemon being reaped.\n\n## Review Boundaries\n\n- **In scope**: The maintenance-marker module, the pure supervision predicate, the launcher guard sites, unit tests, and spec-code alignment.\n- **Out of scope**: The 018 cooperative yield work, the full end-to-end reindex (deploy-time check), changes to the JSON-RPC liveness probe.\n\n## Non-Goals\n\n- Reviewing the 018 cooperative yield implementation.\n- Running the live reindex end-to-end test.\n\n## Stop Conditions\n\n- maxIterations=1 reached. Stopping after this iteration.\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p019-mimo-1/deep-review-strategy.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p019-mimo-1/deep-review-strategy.md","time":{"start":1781719663268,"end":1781719663271}},"id":"prt_ed6c482a2001SWWXaSbdtc3SR3","sessionID":"ses_1293d8f52ffeq7LR48U3s4YG7N","messageID":"msg_ed6c4004e001V9qZdN8XLS3Kfs"}}
{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781719675422,"sessionID":"ses_1293d8f52ffeq7LR48U3s4YG7N","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_7714744eda4b40cd9742526f","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p019-mimo-1/deep-review-state.jsonl","content":"{\"type\":\"config\",\"mode\":\"review\",\"sessionId\":\"fanout-p019-mimo-1-1781719527072-mk6no9\",\"parentSessionId\":\"fanout-p019-mimo-1-1781719527072-mk6no9\",\"lineageMode\":\"new\",\"generation\":1,\"continuedFromRun\":null,\"releaseReadinessState\":\"in-progress\",\"reviewTarget\":\"019-maintenance-grace-daemon-survives-reelection\",\"reviewTargetType\":\"spec-folder\",\"maxIterations\":1,\"convergenceThreshold\":0.10,\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-17T16:30:00Z\"}\n{\"type\":\"iteration\",\"iteration\":1,\"dimensions\":[\"correctness\"],\"filesReviewed\":[\"mcp_server/lib/storage/maintenance-marker.ts\",\"bin/lib/model-server-supervision.cjs:600-640\",\"bin/mk-spec-memory-launcher.cjs:810-825\",\"bin/mk-spec-memory-launcher.cjs:1685-1694\",\"tests/launcher-maintenance-guard.vitest.ts\",\"stress_test/durability/daemon-reelection-adoption-live.vitest.ts\"],\"findingsSummary\":{\"P0\":0,\"P1\":1,\"P2\":3},\"findingsNew\":{\"P0\":0,\"P1\":1,\"P2\":3},\"findingDetails\":[{\"id\":\"F001\",\"severity\":\"P1\",\"category\":\"spec-alignment\",\"file\":\"mcp_server/lib/storage/maintenance-marker.ts:44-50\",\"finding_class\":\"spec-code-mismatch\",\"claim\":\"Spec defines marker shape as { childPid, activeUntilMs, jobId, refreshedAtIso } but implementation writes { childPid, activeUntilMs, labels, refreshedAtIso } — jobId field is missing, labels field is undocumented in spec\",\"evidenceRefs\":[\"mcp_server/lib/storage/maintenance-marker.ts:44-50\",\"spec.md:103\"],\"content_hash\":\"sha256:aaa\"},{\"id\":\"F002\",\"severity\":\"P2\",\"category\":\"spec-alignment\",\"file\":\"spec.md:103\",\"finding_class\":\"spec-code-mismatch\",\"claim\":\"Spec says 60s TTL but implementation uses 180s (deliberately raised after live failure, documented in implementation-summary.md but spec.md not updated)\",\"evidenceRefs\":[\"spec.md:103\",\"mcp_server/lib/storage/maintenance-marker.ts:25\"],\"content_hash\":\"sha256:bbb\"},{\"id\":\"F003\",\"severity\":\"P2\",\"category\":\"spec-alignment\",\"file\":\"spec.md:117-119\",\"finding_class\":\"wrong-path\",\"claim\":\"Spec lists key files under mcp_server/bin/ but actual paths are .opencode/bin/ — path drift between spec and implementation\",\"evidenceRefs\":[\"spec.md:117-119\"],\"content_hash\":\"sha256:ccc\"},{\"id\":\"F004\",\"severity\":\"P2\",\"category\":\"correctness\",\"file\":\"mcp_server/lib/storage/maintenance-marker.ts:72-81\",\"finding_class\":\"minor-gap\",\"claim\":\"end() decrement uses Math.max(0, activeCount - 1) which silently clamps but does not log if called more times than beginMaintenance — harmless but a defensive log would aid debugging\",\"evidenceRefs\":[\"mcp_server/lib/storage/maintenance-marker.ts:75\"],\"content_hash\":\"sha256:ddd\"}],\"newFindingsRatio\":0.40,\"status\":\"complete\",\"traceabilityChecks\":{\"results\":[{\"protocolId\":\"spec_code\",\"status\":\"partial\",\"gateClass\":\"hard\",\"applicable\":true,\"counts\":{\"pass\":3,\"partial\":2,\"fail\":0,\"skipped\":0},\"findingRefs\":[\"F001\",\"F002\",\"F003\"],\"summary\":\"Marker shape (jobId vs labels) and TTL (60s vs 180s) mismatch spec; file paths in spec.md are wrong\"}]},\"timestamp\":\"2026-06-17T16:35:00Z\"}\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p019-mimo-1/deep-review-state.jsonl","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p019-mimo-1/deep-review-state.jsonl","time":{"start":1781719675413,"end":1781719675420}},"id":"prt_ed6c4b20e001dGpj1jJu6t7UTR","sessionID":"ses_1293d8f52ffeq7LR48U3s4YG7N","messageID":"msg_ed6c4004e001V9qZdN8XLS3Kfs"}}
