{"type":"tool_use","timestamp":1781719715946,"sessionID":"ses_1293d8f52ffeq7LR48U3s4YG7N","part":{"type":"tool","tool":"write","callID":"call_f04e9a76067640c79d58eb17","state":{"status":"completed","input":{"filePath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p019-mimo-1/deep-review-dashboard.md","content":"# Deep Review Dashboard\n\n**Target**: 019-maintenance-grace-daemon-survives-reelection\n**Status**: CONDITIONAL | **hasAdvisories**: true\n**Session**: fanout-p019-mimo-1-1781719527072-mk6no9\n**Executor**: cli-opencode (xiaomi/mimo-v2.5-pro)\n\n## Findings Summary\n\n| Severity | Count | Delta |\n|----------|-------|-------|\n| P0 | 0 | — |\n| P1 | 1 | +1 |\n| P2 | 3 | +3 |\n\n## Progress Table\n\n| Iter | Focus | Ratio | Findings | Status |\n|------|-------|-------|----------|--------|\n| 1 | Correctness | 0.40 | 1P1 + 3P2 | complete |\n\n## Coverage\n\n- **Dimensions**: 1/4 complete (Correctness)\n- **Files reviewed**: 6\n- **Traceability**: spec_code=partial, checklist_evidence=skipped (no checklist.md)\n\n## Trend\n\n- Ratios: [0.40] — single iteration, no trend yet\n\n## Active Risks\n\n- **P1 spec-code alignment**: marker shape (jobId vs labels) and TTL (60s vs 180s) mismatch spec\n- **maxIterations reached**: 1/1 iterations used, stopping\n"},"output":"Wrote file successfully.","metadata":{"diagnostics":{},"filepath":"/Users/michelkerkmeester/MEGA/Development/Code_Environment/Public/.opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p019-mimo-1/deep-review-dashboard.md","exists":false,"truncated":false},"title":".opencode/specs/system-spec-kit/027-xce-research-based-refinement/002-memory-store-and-search/review/lineages/p019-mimo-1/deep-review-dashboard.md","time":{"start":1781719715940,"end":1781719715944}},"id":"prt_ed6c55060001Ig5MvsaUsT2eOx","sessionID":"ses_1